  <brief_title>The Effect of Applying Modified NUTRIC Scoring System to Evaluate the Nutrition Risk and Giving Different Types of Nutritional Support on Clinical Outcomes in Critically Ill Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Applying Modified NUTRIC Scoring System to Evaluate the Nutrition Risk and Giving Different Types of Nutritional Support on Clinical Outcomes in Critically Ill Patients</official_title>
